  <official_title>A Randomised, Double Blind Trial to Assess the Pharmacokinetics of Arimidex Alone, Nolvadex Alone, or Arimidex and Nolvadex in Combination, When Used as Adjuvant Treatment for Breast Cancer in Postmenopausal Women</official_title>
